data.description: This beautiful craftsman style home, located in a quiet neighborhood, feels just like home the moment you step onto the front porch. Once inside, the entry invites you into the open concept living space featuring a wood burning fireplace and windows that overlook the patio and large private corner lot. The high-end details are everywhere... coffered ceilings, built-in display shelving, large owner’s suite on the first floor.  The kitchen and dining area are also on full display, so the chef in the family can stay in the mix.  With beautiful white cabinetry and granite countertops, this kitchen lacks for nothing.  The upstairs features a large loft/bonus room along with 4 bedrooms and 2 baths.      The home has fresh wall paint, newly installed tile and LVT flooring. Comes with a transferable home warranty!  Don’t miss the opportunity to have a home where you can create the space of your dreams!
